race.comment: SPEED BYTE (2) copped a check in the run and finished a well held 5.5 lengths third (23.02) last time in a Novice race at this track over 400m. Has the ability and looks a key chance. LOCHINVAR LORD (7) has a strong overall record having two wins and five places from 10 starts including a last start third (22.96) over 400m at this track. Will go close here with a clear run. JAFFA'S MONELLI (8) jumped favourite and was too quick with an all-the-way win last start (22.67) at this track in a Novice race over 400m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. CATHY'S GIRL (1) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.
